added.description: After struggling to solve a riddle from Riddler's helicopter Quizz, Redbird must learn to speak up and share his ideas with the Batwheels if they hope to figure out the villain's true scheme.

added.title: Zoomsday
added.description: The Legion of Zoom is tired of always losing. They decide to take a page from the Batwheels and try using teamwork in order to pull off a daring heist. But will they be able to work together?

added.title: Rev and Let Rev
added.description: Redbird sacrifices his stealth muffler tech to sound as loud as the other Batwheels but his modifications backfire when Robin needs his stealthy skills to catch the elusive Catwoman!

added.title: Batcomputer for a Day
added.description: When Batcomputer shuts down for a system update, the other Batwheels must take over for her while aiding Batman in a battle against Harley Quinn.

added.title: Grass is Greener
added.description: MOE wants to know what it's like to be a member of the Batwheels, but the bot gets more than he bargained for when Bam invites him along for an exciting mission to stop Poison Ivy.

added.title: Holidays on Ice
added.description: Frustrated by the Batwheels' holiday distractions, Batwing decides to "go solo" to thwart Mr. Freeze's evil Christmas-time plot. But Batwing soon realizes how hard it is to stop Mr. Freeze on her own!

added.title: Brand New Track
added.description: Thomas and Percy explore a brand-new track the evening before the route is opened. Everything seems new and exciting, and even a night spent stuck in the mud turns into a wonderful experience. Only in the light of day do they realize that nothing they saw was really "new" at all - it just seemed so because they brought to it a sense of delight and discovery.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Stink Monster
added.description: Thomas and the other young engines encounter a stink monster that threatens to spread a stench all over Knapford! When Percy is kidnapped by the stink monster, the rest of the Biggest Adventure Club band together to create a plan to save their friend and stop the stink monster in its tracks! Looking closer, they realize it's their good friend Whiff's new invention causing a stink!
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Whiteout!
added.description: With the holidays just around the corner, Thomas and Percy are determined to deliver the mail to all the patrons of Sodor. There are presents! The problem is there's a massive whiteout snowstorm covering the entire island and preventing the engines from seeing where they're going. Overcoming various obstacles, Thomas and Percy learn that they can rely on their other senses as well as their familiarity with the island to find where they need to go and deliver the gifts just in time.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Christmas Mountain
added.description: It's Christmas time in Sodor and every engine is excitedly preparing for the holiday, especially Bruno who is excited to put his star on the tree. It's his tradition! When the Christmas tree can't be delivered, Thomas and Percy learn why traditions are important to Bruno. They get creative to keep a disappointed Bruno's holiday spirit bright, ultimately transforming Lookout Mountain into the best -- and biggest -- replacement "tree!" Thomas, Percy, and Bruno are joined by their friends to decorate, sing, and celebrate the tradition together!
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Good as New
added.description: While out on a delivery to Whiff's Recycling Plant with his beloved buddy Boxy in tow, Thomas realizes that his pal is on his last crooked axle. Inspired by Whiff's talent in turning junk into useful inventions, Thomas recruits Percy to help him on a scrap scavenger hunt so they can make Boxy as good as new! However, mending the broken boxcar proves to be harder than Thomas thought, but with guidance from Whiff and his "secret formula," Thomas and friends reduce, reuse, recycle, and rethink to transform Boxy into a rolling repurposed wonder!
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: More Than a Pretty Engine
added.description: After a fierce storm causes a rockslide in Crumble Canyon, mountain engine Ashima is eager to clean and clear the chaos with her new friends. However, Thomas and the others are concerned: if Ashima were to help them, the mucky mess could ruin her beautiful paint! When the friends' fussiness prevents Ashima from working with the team, she has to prove to Thomas and the others that they shouldn't judge her by her appearance.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: More Cowbell
added.description: Thomas is elated when he finds a cowbell on the side of the tracks, until his friends start hogging it.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Halloween Party
added.description: D.BO wonders how do you throw the best Halloween party ever?

added.title: Christmas Scavenger Hunt
added.description: Blippi wonders what is the best part about Christmas?

added.title: Blippi Saves Christmas
added.description: Blippi wonders how does Santa know where we live?

added.title: Penguins
added.description: Blippi wonders can penguins fly?

added.title: Meet the Batwheels
added.description: An action-packed music video of the Batwheels' most exciting adventures set to an extended version of the series' theme song.

added.title: Calling All Batwheels
added.description: A music video introducing all of Batman's heroic vehicle squad - the Batwheels - showcasing their incredible gadgets, stunning talents, and unique personalities.

added.title: Bam!
added.description: Set to his rocking theme song, Bam the Batmobile takes to the streets of Gotham and uses his smarts, leadership skills, and awesome gadgets to fight crime and stop the villainous Legion of Zoom.

added.title: Buff Tuff
added.description: In this country-inspired music video, Buff the Bat-Truck shows off his strength as he tows the bad guys out of town and lifts the spirits of his fellow Batwheels with his sensitive side, all while protecting the people (and critters) of Gotham.

added.title: Faster
added.description: It's time to go, go, go with Batgirl's motorbike Bibi as she zigs and zags her way to victory in this high-energy music video - it doesn't matter if it's a stunt jump or a speeding supervillain, Bibi always gives it her all and then some!

added.title: Fly
added.description: Tour the glittering night sky with Batwing, Gotham's flying protector with a penchant for posing, as she dips, dives, and dodges through buildings and water to take on villains and bail out a friend or two - set to her funky-fresh theme song.

added.title: Spooky Batcave
added.description: A series of spooky sounds and sights leads the Batwheels to believe that the Batcave is haunted by a B-B-Bat-Ghost!

added.title: Robin's Ride
added.description: Robin's ride Redbird is on the case in this radical music video, as he sneaks and sleuths his way to stop Gotham's villains with his speed and detective skills - it's no mystery why Redbird is one of the best!

added.title: Wheelin' and Dealin'
added.description: After losing one of his wheels on his way to stop Prank, Bam comically attempts to replace his tire with all sorts of zany objects while chasing the prankster van around the city.

added.title: Interview with a Crime-Fighter
added.description: Batman discusses the Batmobile's amazing capabilities and features during an interview at Gotham's auto show, featuring impressive clips of Bam in action as he swoops in to save the day.

added.title: The Best Present in the World
added.description: A heart-warming holiday-themed music video where the Batwheels sing about what's most important to them - friendship.

added.title: Diesel's Seagull
added.description: While making a delivery, Diesel comes upon a lost baby seagull, who needs help finding his mama.
added.seriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Kana and the Butterflies
added.description: Kana and Nia are searching for a giant butterfly named the Sodor Skipper.
added.seriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Diesel's Rules
added.description: Diesel tries to race Kana, but he changes the rules multiple times to try to gain an upper hand.
added.seriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Surprise!
added.description: Percy and Diesel are playing a game named Hide and Surprise, but Diesel just can't seem to get the jump on Percy.

added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Confetti Car Kerfuffle
added.description: Everyone loves confetti! The confetti car needs to be delivered to surprise Sir Topham Hatt.
added.seriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Red Light, Green Light
added.description: Thomas, Nia, and Diesel learn about the importance of safety while playing a game of "Red Light, Green Light."

added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Sandy Tidies Up
added.description: Carly attempts to help Sandy recycle some of her many piles of stuff.

added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Lighthouse Disco
added.description: When Diesel and Thomas aren't careful about carrying lightbulbs on flatbeds, they end up mixing their deliveries.

added.title: Percy's Perfect Place
added.description: Percy tries to find a cozy spot to nap and runs away from a family of skunks.

added.title: Skiff Upon the Sea
added.description: Skiff attempts to sail further than he ever has before, all the way to the Vicarstown lighthouse!
